import { NgModule } from '@angular/core';
import { BrowserModule } from '@angular/platform-browser';

import { AppRoutingModule } from './app-routing.module';
import { AppComponent } from './app.component';
import { SignUpComponent } from './pages/sign-up/sign-up.component';
import { SignInComponent } from './pages/sign-in/sign-in.component';
import { HomeComponent } from './pages/home/home.component';
import { FormsModule, ReactiveFormsModule } from '@angular/forms';
import { HttpClientModule, HTTP_INTERCEPTORS } from '@angular/common/http';
import { AuthInterceptor } from './utils/auth.interceptor';
import { ProfileComponent } from './pages/profile/profile.component';
import { AnimeComponent } from './pages/anime/anime.component';
import { MangaComponent } from './pages/manga/manga.component';
import { ForumComponent } from './pages/forum/forum.component';
import { NgxPaginationModule } from 'ngx-pagination';
import { NoDescriptionPipe } from './pipes/no-description.pipe';
import { NoImagePipe } from './pipes/no-image.pipe';
import { NoYearPipe } from './pipes/no-year.pipe';
import { NoSeasonPipe } from './pipes/no-season.pipe';
import { NavComponent } from './components/nav/nav.component';
import { NavfooterComponent } from './components/navfooter/navfooter.component';
import { AnimemodalComponent } from './components/animemodal/animemodal.component';
import { MangamodalComponent } from './components/mangamodal/mangamodal.component';
import { ServiceWorkerModule } from '@angular/service-worker';
import { environment } from '../environments/environment';

@NgModule({
  declarations: [
    AppComponent,
    SignUpComponent,
    SignInComponent,
    HomeComponent,
    ProfileComponent,
    AnimeComponent,
    MangaComponent,
    ForumComponent,
    NoDescriptionPipe,
    NoImagePipe,
    NoYearPipe,
    NoSeasonPipe,
    NavComponent,
    NavfooterComponent,
    AnimemodalComponent,
    MangamodalComponent
  ],
  imports: [
    BrowserModule,
    AppRoutingModule,
    ReactiveFormsModule,
    HttpClientModule,
    NgxPaginationModule,
    FormsModule,
    ServiceWorkerModule.register('ngsw-worker.js', {
      enabled: environment.production,
      // Register the ServiceWorker as soon as the app is stable
      // or after 30 seconds (whichever comes first).
      registrationStrategy: 'registerWhenStable:30000'
    })
  ],
  providers: [{ provide: HTTP_INTERCEPTORS, useClass: AuthInterceptor, multi: true }],
  bootstrap: [AppComponent]
})
export class AppModule { }
